---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base title="About" description="Better Out Co. is a Cape Town company founded by Laura Weyel, bringing the first mould-free, lab-tested coffee enema to South Africa.">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 pt-16 sm:pt-24 pb-12">
    <div class="label text-kraft mb-4">About</div>
    <h1 class="display text-5xl sm:text-6xl text-coffee leading-[1.02] mb-8">
      Better out than in.
    </h1>
    <p class="prose-body italic text-coffee/80 mb-12">
      A founder note from Laura — Cape Town, 2026.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 prose-body text-coffee/90 space-y-6 pb-20">
    <p>
      Better Out Co. began the way most honest things do — quietly, in a kitchen, after years of trying everything else first. I'd read the labels, swapped the pans, filtered the water, fed my family in the way I'd come to believe in. But there was one tool I kept circling back to, one practice that genuinely changed how I felt: the coffee enema.
    </p>
    <p>
      And every time I went looking for it locally, I found the same problem. Mouldy coffee, vague sourcing, no testing, no one taking it seriously. The very thing meant to lighten the liver's load was, more often than not, adding to it.
    </p>
    <p>
      So I made the version I wished existed. Organic. Lab-tested. Guaranteed mould-free. Paired with a clean, well-made kit. The first of its kind in South Africa.
    </p>

    <hr class="hairline my-10" />

    <p class="display text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-coffee leading-snug !mb-2">
      The library is part of the work.
    </p>
    <p>
      The five free guides on this site aren't a lead magnet — they're the worldview. Steady energy, real food, a lighter load, and healing at the root. The coffee enema is only one chapter of that bigger story, and it makes the most sense once the rest is in place.
    </p>
    <p>
      Read what calls to you. Take one small thing at a time. There's no prize for taking years.
    </p>

    <hr class="hairline my-10" />

    <p class="font-serif italic text-coffee/70">
      With care,<br/>
      Laura<br/>
      <span class="label text-coffee/55 mt-2 inline-block">Founder · Cape Town</span>
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-cream-soft/40 border-y border-coffee/10">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 py-14 text-center">
      <h2 class="display text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-coffee mb-5">Say hello.</h2>
      <p class="prose-body text-coffee/75 mb-7">
        The shop opens soon. Until then, the best place to chat is Instagram — that's where we share the build, the lab results, and the launch date.
      </p>
      <a href="https://instagram.com/better.out.co" rel="me noopener" class="btn-coffee">@better.out.co</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
